Question.Subject: http://intmail.183.com.cn/item/itemStatusQuery.do?lan=0?
Question.Content: i need some information about this website?
Question.ChosenAnswer: Actually this website is where u can track your order from alibaba.com or aliexpress.com. which they send your parcel by the china post.you can go directly to this web (intmail.183.com.cn)to check your parcel online . I have order an electric guitar by the alibaba.com two weeks ago..they post the guitar on 20/03/2010 to Brunei Darussalam,and give me the tracking no CP164277077CN .i received the item on 29/03/2010.
